@startuml distillation-flow
title PetBox distillation — when / what / which entity  (digest slice BUILT: SessionDigestJob -> session-digests; typed-facts autocapture still an idea)
skinparam shadowing false

start
:Trigger;
note right
  WHEN (any of):
  - session append / close  (autocapture, idea)
  - scheduled batch  (off-peak)
  - on-demand  (operator / hook)
end note

:Select source episode;
note right
  WHICH ENTITY:
  - episodic sessions (raw Claude transcripts)  [primary]
  - (later) board comments / activity
  only UN-distilled or changed episodes
end note

if (Chat LLM available?\nDeepSeek, infer=true) then (no)
  :defer / requeue;
  stop
else (yes)
  :LLM extract candidate facts;
  note right
    WHAT GOES IN (durable only):
    - decision + WHY
    - fixed-bug root cause
    - convention / gotcha
    - stated preference
    typed: User | Feedback | Project | Reference
    NOT raw narration / derivable-from-code
  end note
endif

:Dedup vs existing memory.*;
note right
  semantic + lexical;
  embedder down -> lexical-only dedup
end note

:Write fact to semantic tier (memory.*);
:Attach PROVENANCE (sessionId + offset);
note right
  the "one mega-session" bridge:
  found by meaning -> drill down to verbatim source
end note

:Mark episode distilled;
stop
@enduml
